eal%20benefit%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwouldn't%20rule%20out%26quot%3B%20including%20it%20in%20a%20self-driving%20vehicle's%20multi-sensor%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20LiDAR%20started%20during%20an%20earlier%20development%20period%2C%20when%20the%20models%20being%20run%20had%20trouble%20processing%20inputs%20from%20different%20sensors%20and%20cameras%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20what's%20happened%20is%20that%20we%20no%20longer%20run%20the%20models%20like%20that.%20So%20the%20models%20benefit%20from%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20information%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaringe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20LiDAR%20used%20to%20be%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20It's%20now%20low%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20great%20sensor%20that%20can%20do%20things%20that%20cameras%20can't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Scaringe%20at%20Rivian%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaringe's%20view%20differs%20from%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20LiDAR%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Musk%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20that%20using%20LiDAR%20and%20radar%20alongside%20cameras%20results%20in%20%26quot%3Bsensor%20contention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sensor%20ambiguity%20causes%20increased%2C%20not%20decreased%2C%20risk.%20That's%20why%20Waymos%20can't%20drive%20on%20highways%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20on%20X%20on%20August%2025%2C%20referencing%20the%20robotaxi%20service%20owned%20by%20Google's%20parent%20company%2C%20Alphabet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20self-driving%20vehicles%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emulti-sensor%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20comprising%20LiDAR%2C%20radar%2C%20and%20cameras%20to%20perceive%20their%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20instead%20betting%20its%20hopes%20on%20a%20vision-only%20system%20that%20relies%20on%20cameras%2C%20Musk%20said%20at%20Tesla's%20%26quot%3BAutonomy%20Day%26quot%3B%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20cars%2C%20it's%20friggin%20stupid.%20It's%20expensive%20and%20unnecessary.%20Once%20you%20solve%20vision%2C%20it's%20worthless%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaringe%20isn't%20the%20only%20auto%20executive%20who%20disagrees%20with%20Musk%20on%20LiDAR.%20In%20June%2C%20Ford%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-china-completely-dominating-tesla-gm-ford-ev-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJim%20Farley%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20at%20the%20Aspen%20Ideas%20Festival%20that%20LiDAR%20was%20%26quot%3Bmission%20critical%26quot%3B%20for%20achieving%20autonomous%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20said%20LiDAR%20would%20be%20more%20effective%20than%20cameras%20when%20driving%20in%20places%20with%20bright%20sunlight.%20While%20the%20camera%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20completely%20blinded%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20LiDAR%20system%20will%20still%20be%20able%20to%20monitor%20its%20surroundings%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20trust%20Ford%2C%20and%20when%20you%20have%20a%20brand%20like%20Ford%2C%20when%20there's%20a%20new%20technology%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20really%20careful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-ceo-tesla-cameras-self-driving-cars-need-lidar-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759808285000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e471d91c1f80efbec50945%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%2