ught%20Jony%20Ive's%20startup%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20sparked%20speculation%20on%20what%20AI%20gadgets%20OpenAI%20could%20release%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Ive%20said%20he%20has%20many%20ideas%20for%20OpenAI's%20family%20of%20AI%20devices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsir-jony-ive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJony%20Ive%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%2015%20to%2020%20ideas%20for%20OpenAI's%20family%20of%20AI%20devices%2C%20and%20they%20will%20likely%20be%20nothing%20like%20an%20iPhone%2C%20he%20told%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjony-ive-device-openai-io-guesses-sam-altman-chatgpt-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20startup's%20DevDay%20conference%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20criticized%20smartphones%20and%20tablets%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20the%20very%20devices%20he%20made%20famous%20%E2%80%94%20during%20the%20talk%20and%20said%20he%20hopes%20these%20new%20AI%20devices%20will%20make%20humans%20happier%20and%20less%20anxious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20said%20we%20have%20an%20uncomfortable%20relationship%20with%20our%20technology%2C%20I%20mean%20that's%20the%20most%20obscene%20understatement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ive%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple's%20former%20chief%20designer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20not%20just%20redress%20that%2C%20but%20absolutely%20change%20the%20situation%20that%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in.%20That%20we%20don't%20accept%20this%20has%20to%20be%20the%20norm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Altman%2C%20who%20acted%20as%20interviewer%20at%20the%20event%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20bought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohnny-ive-openai-chatgpt-distribution-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIve's%20device%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20for%20more%20than%20%246%20billion.%20That%20sparked%20speculation%20about%20what%20AI%20gadgets%20the%20former%20Apple%20designer%20is%20working%20on.%20Altman%20previously%20discussed%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20AI%20companion%20as%20well%20as%20an%20entire%20family%20of%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20OpenAI%20and%20Ive's%20design%20chops%20poses%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20Apple%2C%20which%20has%20dominated%20the%20mobile%20era%20but%20lags%20behind%20in%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20said%20progress%20is%20so%20swift%20right%20now%20that%20it's%20hard%20for%20him%20and%20his%20design%20team%20to%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20momentum%C2%A0has%20led%20us%20to%20create%2015%20to%2020%20really%20compelling%20product%20ideas.%20The%20challenge%20is%20to%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Ive%20told%20Altman%20onstage.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20easy%20if%20you%20knew%20there%20are%20three%20good%20ones.%20It's%20just%20not%20like%20that.%20We're%20designing%20a%20family%20of%20products.%20And%20we're%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20judicious%20and%20thoughtful%20in%20what%20we%20focus%20on%20and%20to%20then%20not%20be%20distracted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%20said%20he%20hopes%20the%20devices%20will%20be%20fun%20and%20address%20some%20of%20the%20issues%20smartphones%20and%20tablets%20have%20created%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ramifications%20and%20consequences%20of%20not%20caring%20and%20not%20being%20careful%20are%20truly%20horrendous%2C%26quot%3B%20Ive%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20the%20interfaces%20we%20design%2C%20if%20we%20can't%20smile%20honestly%2C%20if%20it's%20just%20another%20deeply%20serious%20exclusive%20thing%2C%20I%20think%20that%20would%20do%20us%20all%20a%20huge%20disservice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20have%20been%20another%20dig%20at%20Apple%2C%20which%20is%20super%20seri