in%20AI%20at%20Northeastern%20University%20in%202023%2C%20the%20AI%20job%20market%20was%20a%20world%20away%20from%20the%20red-hot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-meta-tried-poaching-openai-staff-ai-talent-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20talent%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20are%20waging%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20an%20applied%20scientist%20at%20Amazon%20after%20interning%20there%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022.%20This%20was%20before%20the%20company%20implemented%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-reportedly-freezes-hiring-for-its-global-retail-business-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiring%20freeze%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20top-flight%20AI%20researcher%20with%20a%20Ph.D.%20could%20see%20themselves%20scoring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-1-million-pay-packages-tech-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emillion-dollar%20payday%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20companies%20like%20Meta.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20road%20to%20earning%20a%20Ph.D.%20isn't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20demands%20lots%20of%20discipline%20and%20motivation.%20In%20fact%2C%20during%20one%20of%20my%20semesters%2C%20I%20was%20so%20caught%20up%20with%20coursework%20and%20research%20that%20I%20barely%20had%20time%20to%20eat.%20I%20ended%20up%20creating%20a%20simple%20stew%20and%20eating%20it%20week%20after%20week%20for%20the%20entire%20school%20term.%20It%20was%20just%20that%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20on%20top%20of%20the%20time%20taken.%20A%20Ph.D.%20candidate%20could%20spend%20about%20five%20years%20trying%20to%20complete%20it.%20That%20time%20could%20have%20been%20spent%20gaining%20practical%20experience%20in%20the%20working%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7168a85-dad0-4f5d-b3d6-8ad6de982508%5C%22%3EGetting%20a%20Ph.D%20is%20challenging%20but%20rewarding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20to%20be%20gained%20from%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-work-at-openai-curiosity-grit-matter-more-than-phd-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPh.D.%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20you%20could%20try%20to%20self-learn%20about%20the%20field%20through%20on-the-job%20training.%20You%20might%20even%20get%20to%20build%20some%20products%20yourself.%20But%20if%20you%20want%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20AI%2C%20you%20need%20to%20do%20a%20Ph.D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20through%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20a%20Ph.D.%20will%20make%20your%20learning%20process%20a%20lot%20more%20structured%20and%20precise.%20That%20has%20become%20very%20important%20now%2C%20given%20how%20competitive%20AI%20research%20has%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%2010%20to%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20small%20change%20or%20tweak%20to%20a%20model%20would%20produce%20different%20results%20that%20could%20land%20you%20in%20a%20prestigious%20journal%20or%20an%20invitation%20to%20a%20high-level%20conference.%20That's%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20has%20become%20much%20higher.%20You%20need%20to%20conduct%20more%20experiments%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20results%20that%20generalize%20well%20across%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ee92339-4cb8-45bc-a546-f8c62f93351e%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20too%20late%20to%20get%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20AI%20is%20progressing%20so%20rapidly%20that%20it%20may%20be%20too%20late%20to%20enter%20the%20field%20through%20the%20Ph.D.%20route.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-team-too-late-phd-ai-hype-jad-tarifi-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDetractors%20believe%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20the%20innovations%20and%20breakthroughs%20in%20AI%20might%20be%20discovered%20by%20the%20time%20you%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20disagree%20with%20that%20view.%20A%20Ph.D.%20in%20AI%20will%20be%20just%20as%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20relevant%2050%20years%20from%20now.%20This%20is%20because%20AI%20will%20become%20ubiquitous%20in%20our%20daily%20lives.%20They%20could%20be%20embedded%20in%20almost%20any%20code%20we%20write%20and%20the%20systems%20around%20us.%20You%20will%20need%20more%2C%20not%20fewer%2C%20people%20who%20can%20understand%20and%20work%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20systems%20aren't%20perfect.%20Their%20algorithms%20might%20break%20in%20the%20future%2C%20and%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20you%20will%20need%20people%20who%20understand%20AI%20at%20a%20fundamental%20level%20to%20come%20in%20and%20fix%20it.%20That's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20someone%20who%20holds%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20owning%20a%20car.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20perfectly%20nice%20car%2C%20but%20you%20will%20still%20need%20to%20train%20mechanics%20to%20fix%20it%20when%20it%20breaks%20down.%20We%20didn't%20stop%20teaching%20mechanical%20and%20automotive%20engineering%20just%20because%20we%20can%20make%20better%20cars.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22334a663b-06da-454a-a223-18437b93046d%5C%22%3EIndustry%20internships%20are%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20highly%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-fight-hunger-games-style-for-top-banking-jobs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoing%20internships%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20summer%20breaks%20in%20between%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-decide-getting-phd-doctorate-degree-right-career-move-costs-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPh.D.%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20matters%20even%20if%20you%20intend%20to%20stay%20in%20academia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20case%2C%20I%20did%20three%20internships%2C%20with%20the%20Bosch%20Center%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and