20days%2C%20Demir%20was%20up%20at%204%20a.m.%20for%20global%20calls%20while%20I%20ran%20digital%20marketing.%20It%20was%20intense%2C%20but%20we%20thrived%20on%20testing%2C%20listening%2C%20and%20refining.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-bali-workcation-struggles-work-tourists-friends-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBali's%20culture%20of%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20shaped%20our%20company's%20philosophy.%20People%20we%20met%20in%20Bali%20didn't%20work%20all%20day%3B%20they%20made%20time%20for%20family%2C%20community%2C%20and%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20corporate%20world%20obsessed%20with%20hustle%2C%20this%20was%20a%20radical%20shift.%20We%20integrated%20that%20mindset%20into%20our%20work%20with%20clients%2C%20helping%20them%20create%20schedules%20that%20protected%20their%20health%20and%20allowed%20room%20for%20joy.%20While%20living%20in%20Bali%2C%20we%20even%20had%20time%20to%20take%20side%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESettling%20into%20our%20new%20home%20was%20an%20adventure%20in%20itself.%20Getting%20around%20meant%20navigating%20chaotic%20streets%20on%20scooters%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20hit%20like%20a%20wall.%20Rainstorms%20were%20a%20daily%20surprise%2C%20so%20we%20always%20had%20ponchos%20ready.%20But%20the%20rewards%20included%20great%20food%2C%20daily%20coffee%20rituals%2C%20and%20a%20perfectly%20unhurried%20pace%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carey%20and%20Demir%20Bentley%20started%20their%20family%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e34c481c1f80efbec4f5b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20started%20their%20family%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia%20%E2%80%94%20Bentley%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20local%20healthcare%20system.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Carey%20Bentley%3C