0the%20AI%20company's%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%20is%20spreading%20OpenAI's%20chips%20around%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ChatGPT-maker%20said%20Monday%20that%20it%20had%20agreed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-amd-chips-deal-nvidia-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emulti-year%20deal%20with%20AMD%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20it%20will%20deploy%20chips%20requiring%20up%20to%20six%20gigawatts%20of%20power.%20The%20deal%20also%20includes%20an%20option%20to%20acquire%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20AMD%20stock%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20just%20weeks%20after%20news%20of%20two%20additional%20deals%20with%20other%20chip%20firms%20last%20month.%20Nvidia%20announced%20that%20OpenAI%20will%20gain%20access%20to%2010%20gigawatts%20of%20high-powered%20GPUs%2C%20alongside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-nvidia-partnership-100b-data-centers-access-power-electricity-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20billion%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20chipmaker.%20And%20OpenAI%20is%20set%20to%20produce%20its%20first%20AI%20chip%20in%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroadcom-nvidia-custom-ai-chips-asics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBroadcom%3C%2Fa%3E%20next%20year.%20OpenAI%20also%20made%20a%20deal%20with%20Oracle%20for%20AI%20compute%20in%20July%2C%20worth%20more%20than%20%24300%20billion%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flurry%20of%20dealmaking%20demonstrates%20how%20OpenAI%20has%20become%20a%20dominant%20force%20in%20the%20chip%20industry%2C%20and%20how%20Altman%20is%20thinking%20long-term%20about%20his%20company's%20access%20to%20the%20hardware%20that%20is%20so%20vital%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20the%20OpenAI%20CEO%20is%20spreading%20its%20piles%20of%20investor%20cash%20among%20chipmaker