ve%2C%20the%20way%20this%20deal%20is%20structured%2C%20to%20succeed%20with%20AMD%2C%26quot%3B%20Newman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dacf7fa2-94ce-499c-a14d-874ef8002408%5C%22%3EIt%20all%20depends%20on%20OpenAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20investing%20in%20competition%20among%20chipmakers%2C%20these%20longer%20deals%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20hearty%20demand%20signal.%20Or%20at%20least%20that's%20the%20hope%20of%20all%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorry%20about%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-bubble-meta-sam-altman-mit-report-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20hype%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20percolating%20throughout%20the%20summer%20and%20into%20the%20fall.%20Deals%20like%20this%20one%20and%20Nvidia's%20eye-watering%20%24100%20billion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20last%20month%20signal%20to%20the%20broader%20market%20that%20the%20infrastructure%20buildout%20of%20data%20centers%20full%20of%20GPUs%20will%20continue%20%E2%80%94%20strongly%20implying%20that%20underneath%20is%20consistent%20growing%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20investment%20underscores%20confidence%20in%20OpenAI's%20long-term%20trajectory%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Post%20of%20Bank%20of%20America%20wrote%20earlier%20this%20month%20in%20reaction%20to%20Nvidia's%20investment%20in%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20while%20concerns%20that%20one%20chipmaker%20holds%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20may%20be%20waning%2C%20OpenAI's%20dominance%20is%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20deals%20are%20only%20good%20business%20if%20OpenAI%20continues%20to%20grow.%20Therefore%2C%20according%20to%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20Stacy%20Rasgon%20of%20Bernstein%2C%20Altman%20%26quot%3Bhas%20the%20power%20to%20crash%20the%20global%20economy%20for%20a%20decade%20or%20take%20us%20all%20to%20the%20promised%20land%20and%20right%20now%20we%20don't%20know%20which%20is%20in%20the%20cards.%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%